Concerning my latest video: There’s a lot that’s been said, a lot I’ve learned, and a lot more I want to say, but I’m exhausted trying to prove my heart and intention to so many people who at the end of the day have probably already formed their own stubborn, negative opinion about me. So this is how I feel in a nutshell ❤️ ~


“Educate me, don’t belittle me”

Our knee jerk reaction to hate on & persecute someone with a seemingly different opinion than ourselves is so toxic. If our opinion has real substance, we can back it up with factual sources. Shouldn’t we try our best to present our beliefs kindly?

~

(This is not about random trolls or people being negative, it’s long time subscribers that I think are misunderstanding my intentions here)

LOVE YOU ALL. THANK YOU FOR YOUR ENCOURAGMENT AND SUPPORT!!! ❤️❤️❤️ I know it’s a flaw in humans to focus on the negative and I’m really trying not to, just difficult sometimes. Especially those who understand anxiety and depression. I may not be made for the limelight or being a big online personality, but I’m trying my best and doing what I can to stay strong and spread kindness. ❤️
